Dress up lessons for Fans to learn how to dress Cute Dolls easily.
Dressup Dolls Babydoll is a dress up game for Dolls very FUN, CREATIVE and ENTERTAINING game! Are you ready to open all big surprises then surprise freinds with cute dolls, enjoy many surprises. Hatch eggs and collect coins to open surprising eggs!ğŸ§

Select your favorite dolls and babydolls then customize her appearance by modifying her hairstyle, eyes, makeup and underwear. You can dress up your favorite dolls for different occasions. Big surprise collection of coats, jackets, t-shirts, sweaters, skirts, trousers, dresses and shoes allows you to come up with unlimited combinations and appearances. In addition, you also have lots of handbags, hats, sunglasses, headsets, jewelry and other accessories to make your cute lol dolls look even prettier and more stylish with bigger surprising dresses.ğŸ£

At the end, you can choose animated scene for your cute doll to appear in, play one of the dressup game or take a photo and show your lovely doll to your friends and surprise them. Ready to Collect eggs then open the surprising eggs!?ğŸ£
